# Do these below before you run the code every time
Follow step by step:
1. Download Ubuntu 22.04.5 LTS (Jammy Jellyfish) (https://releases.ubuntu.com/22.04/ubuntu-22.04.5-desktop-amd64.iso)

2. Follow steps in Appendix A (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XWQjx1A6kYYNf67U3wGeeTDOYbf8WOUC/edit?usp=drive_link&ouid=113432680517543542164&rtpof=true&sd=true)

3. Follow steps in '0 In the beginning.._' file (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1wfj3bDukCwpjZttP-xAIN0m04yM9rxSo/edit?usp=drive_link&ouid=113432680517543542164&rtpof=true&sd=true)
Note 1: Between step 2.2 and step 2.3 in the '0 In the beginning.._' file, you need to start Zookeeper and Kafka as well.
Note 2: Between step 5 and step 6 in the '0 In the beginning.._' file, you need to manually create a folder named "DE" in C:\ drive.
Note 3: After step 7.2 in the '0 In the beginning.._' file, type 'jupyter lab' and click the link appeared in PowerShell.

4. Download all the .py files in all the 6 folders. 

5. Upload all the .py downloaded in the folder 'de-prj'.

6. Open terminal and typing the below one after another after it finished runnning:
python Task1.py
python Task2.py
python Task3.py
python Task4.py
python Task5.py


!!!
To close the jupyter lab, click 'File' and choose 'Shut down'. DO NOT STRAIGHT AWAY CLOSE THE TAB.

After than you will be back to PowerShell, and follow Appendix B (https://docs.google.com/document/d/13kObPws_WnqOCJ3ciZS8xtKgEBanXPdS/edit#heading=h.36jbn1btzee6) 
to stop the Kafka followed by Zookeeper followed YARN and lastly followed by HDFS.

IF ANY STEPS ARE MISSING, IT MIGHT LEAD TO DATA CORRUPTION, PERFORMANCE DEGRADATION OR EVEN EXPOSED SECURITY RISKS.
